        <step>
          <para>Support actuator with sling. Remove actuator attachment bolts and discard.</para>
        </step>
        <step>
          <para>Remove actuator from nose gear bay. Clean mating flanges with lint-free cloth and approved solvent (CPC#443).</para>
        </step>
        <step>
          <para>Install replacement actuator (PN: ACT-NLG-RET-777). Use new bolts and torque to 180 in-lb (Ref: AMM 20-50-00).</para>
        </step>
        <step>
          <para>Reconnect hydraulic lines using new O-rings (MS28775-222). Confirm seating before torquing fittings to spec.</para>
